item.title: CVE-2016-9880|2024-08-06T03:07:30.135Z -- dell%20emc -- gemfire%20broker%20for%20cloud%20foundry
item.description: The GemFire broker for Cloud Foundry 1.6.x before 1.6.5 and 1.7.x before 1.7.1 has multiple API endpoints which do not require authentication and could be used to gain access to the cluster managed by the broker.
